name: A Timeless Moment
description: A moment when you’re together with your lover. In a misfit place yet you don’t care as long as you are together. An evening light shine through the window as you both caress each other’s face. And you feel as if time won’t fly, like you’re paralysed by it. Paralysed by the person next to you. You don’t want anything to change, not even a second to pass, because beyond that moment you know people will judge. People will stare. So in that moment you prayed, you want to stay like that forever.
